OL,5, The UK's aviation watchdog should have 
OL,6, stronger powers to protect passengers  
OL,7, hit by the kind of disruption caused by
OL,8, the pandemic, MPs have recommended.    
OL,10,FThe sector was hit hard by efforts to  
OL,11,Ftackle the virus, including quarantine,
OL,12,Ftesting regimes and travel bans.       
OL,14,FThe Civil Aviation Authority should    
OL,15,Fhave "more teeth" to be able to fine   
OL,16,Fairlines not giving refunds, a Commons 
OL,17,FTransport Committee report said.       
OL,19,FIt also called for ministers to publish
OL,20,Fan aviation recovery plan by June.     
